2 Hours Ago “One group of Nigerian students having been repeatedly refused entry into Poland have concluded they have no choice but to travel again across Ukraine and attempt to exit the country via the border with Hungary. “We understand the pain and fear that is confronting all people who find themselves in this terrifying place. “We also appreciate that those in official positions in security and border management will in most cases be experiencing impossible expectations in a situation they never expected.



